🧩 How to Use This Repo
Start with Level 1  
Learn shapes, rhythms, and simple lunar timing.

Move to Level 2  
Explore mythic timing, Hero/Feminine cycles, and lunar rituals.

Read Level 3  
Discover your sign’s rhythm and personal lunar timing map.

Follow the Medium Series  
Weekly articles deepen your rhythm literacy.

Use the lunar trackers  
Align your timing with real‑time moon phases.

Check the Wiki  
All ProjectCompass knowledge lives there.

